{"tid":910004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<登美列根號航母>CCTVB:戰機靠彈射器起飛，中國也擁有相同技術，會在將來服役的航母應用","createTime":"2018-11-20T23:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T06:55:19.000Z","uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":96,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"7988e1e0b2fed90c54f4fb3c7107ba862a221605","tid":910004,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:23:23.000Z","msg":"解放軍駐港部隊司令員登美航母訪問 列根號明早抵港<br />\n<br />\n2018-11-20 22:05<br />\n<br />\n這艘尼米茲級核動力航空母艦2003年服役，以已故美國總統列根命名。戰機靠彈射器起飛，中國也擁有相同技術，會在將來服役的航母應用。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5bf415eee60383852eefdc95/?lang=cht&amp;is_sd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5bf415eee60383852eefdc95%2F%3Flang%3Dcht%26is_sd&d=urbJlywAQcMBFL9ikkylnl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a055327b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5bf415eee60383852eefdc95/?lang=cht&amp;is_sd</a>"},{"pid":"f9923687f76871c80717f6b8a916d8868165e53d","tid":910004,"uid":57848,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501c3d37a3ffb2f31c25163a5914af9196061d42","tid":910004,"uid":37661,"like":200,"dislike":0,"score":200,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:29:09.000Z","msg":"飛機場港女望着個大波妹：得佢心口有兩嚿肉咩！我夠有咯。<br />\n<br />\n友人問：喺邊呀？<br />\n<br />\n飛機場港女：喺肚腩。"},{"pid":"96a22d1e6f7b0ed57f5188803340cce56541786c","tid":910004,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3a4d03474370048e4925cee381d2dcf002ecbc","tid":910004,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2